name: Phoenix Tree Holdings
short_description: Phoenix Tree Holdings Limited, through its subsidiaries, leases apartments from property owners and rents them to residents and corporate clients in the People's Republic of China.
long_description: Phoenix Tree Holdings Limited, through its subsidiaries, leases apartments from property owners and rents them to residents and corporate clients in the People's Republic of China. It designs, renovates, and furnishes apartments; and provides WiFi, 24/7 resident support, and common area maintenance and utilities to the residents, as well as repair and maintenance for private rooms. As of December 31, 2019, it operated 438,309 apartment units; and nine apartment facilities under the Dream Apartment brand name with a total of 8,558 beds and four additional facilities in Beijing, Shanghai, and Shenzhen. The company was founded in 2015 and is headquartered in Beijing, China.
